		<Subsection Id="2">
			<Text xml:space="preserve" Style="Intro">Notwithstanding the provisions of this section or s. 145.19, district school board members may reduce their salary rate on a voluntary basis.</Text>
		</Subsection>
		<Subsection Id="3">
			<Text xml:space="preserve" Style="Intro">Notwithstanding the provisions of this section and s. 145.19, for the 2010-2011 fiscal year, the salary of each district school board member shall be the amount calculated pursuant to subsection (1) or the district’s beginning salary for teachers who hold baccalaureate degrees, whichever is less.</Text>
